    org.jetbrains.mps.openapi.model.SModelListener, org.jetbrains.mps.openapi.model.SNodeAccessListener, org.jetbrains.mps.openapi.model.SNodeChangeListener, org.jetbrains.mps.openapi.module.SModuleListener, org.jetbrains.mps.openapi.module.SRepositoryAttachListener, org.jetbrains.mps.openapi.module.SRepositoryListener
    public class DataTreeChangesNotifier
extends org.jetbrains.mps.openapi.module.SRepositoryContentAdapter
    Despite the name, not specific to DataTree any longer. Generic change notifier for elements supplied. Use SRepositoryContentAdapter.subscribeTo(SRepository)/SRepositoryContentAdapter.unsubscribeFrom(SRepository) to activate/deactivate change tracking

                       IChangeListener l,
                       @Nullable
                       Set<org.jetbrains.mps.openapi.model.SNodeReference> nodes)
        Tells to notify given listener once any node from the supplied set is changed. Sets of nodes do not add up, two subsequent trackNodes() calls for the same listener would result in first registration being void.
